# Raw geometry exports dropped at the repo root (buildings.stl,
# groundpatched_extrude.stl, ...). These are inputs to
# tools/prepare_case_stl.py — often hundreds of MB — and are converted into the
# committed, domain-frame STL under examples/<case>/. Never commit the raw ones.
/*.stl
/*.STL

